===Etymology===
[[meat]] + [[loaf]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun|meatloaves}}
# A mixture of ground meat (beef, pork, veal, etc., or a combination thereof) mixed with seasonings and vegetables such as onion, formed into a loaf or fitted into a [[loaf pan]] and baked, then served in slices.

